                    <span id="c-1059364040" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1059364040" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1059364040">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55953438/">廿一</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-07-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">义理，在儒家学说中属于德行科，《宋史》所谓的道学，儒家的根本。还有经济，属于政事科；辞章，属于言语科；考据，属于文章科。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1056106441">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
